Title: Lorentz and CPT Violating Chern-Simons Term in the Formulation of

Functional IntegralAuthors: J.-M. Chung

Comments: 5 pages, no figure, RevTex

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D60 (1999) 127901

We show that in the functional integral formalism the (finite) coefficient ofthe induced, Lorentz- and CPT-violating Chern-Simons term, arising from theLorentz- and CPT-violating fermion sector, is undetermined.